name: Canada NFT. Mountain crystal
description: Unique NFT country of Canada. The base is made of precious rock crystal, which has preserved the most beautiful phenomenon - the Northern Lights of Canada (If you look closely, you can see it). Stand in the shape of a hockey puck made of pure gold. On the main stand, with the help of a mechanism, Canadian hockey players hit the puck, on the back of the Maple Leaf emblem, the symbol of Canada.
